As a user I can login and see a list of hairstylists in my area so that I can browse their work.
As I user I want to be able to click on a hair stylist and see their specific posts so that I can see
if they're doing hair the way I'd like mine to be done. As a user I can upvote, or downvote a hair stylist
so that I can give my opinions as to whether or not their services are something that I'd like to employ.  As
a stylist I want to be able to create an account so that I can broadcast my work. As a stylist I want to be able
to create postings so that users can see what I've done with my skills.